    <item>
      <title>Hauser 称即使美国发出降息信号，澳大利亚央行仍将维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/rba-set-to-stand-pat-even-as-us-signals-rate-cuts-hauser-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚央行副行长安德鲁豪泽表示，澳大利亚利率近期可能保持不变，因为通胀“比美国稍微更为棘手”，这凸显了美联储准备放松政策之际全球通胀形势的分化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/rba-set-to-stand-pat-even-as-us-signals-rate-cuts-hauser-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:05:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国大宗商品库存激增 凸显经济放缓严重程度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/china-s-bulging-commodity-stockpiles-lay-depth-of-slowdown-bare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国主要原材料库存不断增加，表明经济活动仍然过于疲软，无法消化造成钢铁、大豆等产品价格暴跌的过剩产能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/china-s-bulging-commodity-stockpiles-lay-depth-of-slowdown-bare</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:01:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储和日本央行利率决议明朗，日元有望上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/yen-forecasts-swing-to-gains-as-fed-boj-offer-rates-clarity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本央行七月份加息以及美联储最近暗示即将削减美国借贷成本之后，货币策略师们对日元的走势进行了彻底的重新思考。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/yen-forecasts-swing-to-gains-as-fed-boj-offer-rates-clarity</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 23:52:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储会议纪要后，台币或将成为亚洲股市反弹的落后者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/taiwan-dollar-likely-a-laggard-in-potential-post-fed-asian-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鉴于台湾的利率处于明显劣势，且本土企业持有美元的动机更强，美联储开始放松政策后，台币在任何反弹中可能再次跑输其他亚洲货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/taiwan-dollar-likely-a-laggard-in-potential-post-fed-asian-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
