    <item>
      <title>英国工党称若维持燃油补贴将面临英镑贬值风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-risked-run-on-pound-if-fuel-subsidy-had-stayed-labour-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国下议院领袖露西·鲍威尔表示，如果财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯不取消 1000 万养老金领取者的冬季燃料补贴以填补公共财政缺口，英国将面临英镑贬值、利率上升和经济危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-risked-run-on-pound-if-fuel-subsidy-had-stayed-labour-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国北海石油游说团体警告暴利税增加将导致投资下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-north-sea-oil-lobby-warns-of-investment-slump-due-to-windfall-tax-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业游说团体警告称，英国针对北海石油和天然气的新税制可能导致投资下降 80% 以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-north-sea-oil-lobby-warns-of-investment-slump-due-to-windfall-tax-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市因中国工厂活动下滑而下滑：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/asia-eyes-cautious-open-after-china-factory-data-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者准备迎接美国政策转变，且中国支持疲弱经济的努力未能奏效，亚洲股市周一下跌。]]></description>
